{"tid":341971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★奴工！女工慘遭機器軋傷3指險斷","createTime":"2017-07-31T08:38:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T11:33:03.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"93d06aeb5839a64021ca2bb072aca3d9c31a8579","tid":341971,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:38:00.000Z","msg":"葵涌發生工業意外。今晨9時許，位於葵榮路40至44號的任合興(葵涌)工業大廈一間廠房，一名姓余(45歲)女工在操作一部茶葉包裝機器時，意外被機器軋傷右手中指、無名指及尾指，她痛極呼救和狂拍機器，工友聞訊大驚，隨即上前協助關掉機器和召救護車，救護員到場為她包紮送院，其後事主報警求助，警方調查後將案列工業意外。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170731/bkn-20170731104829627-0731_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170731%2Fbkn-20170731104829627-0731_00822_001.html&d=yX%2F66xiNI6rdAY%2FZDkS4L3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=a5c35c31\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170731/bkn-20170731104829627-0731_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"23ee5f12a6832adb3e17575ad596ca6e0789863d","tid":341971,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:38:29.000Z","msg":"返工，不了！"},{"pid":"8d6fd33c6a8982359ede8c10a5e0a70d50d2b79d","tid":341971,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T09:50:54.000Z","msg":"少數事件"},{"pid":"329587748a7ae0eee5f1a9273c81a861d7f08ab6","tid":341971,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T10:01:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>少數事件</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d5e1dd2daf02faf1ff1585a47c7cd7ca4d567f9","tid":341971,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:13:37.000Z","msg":"都係返工好"},{"pid":"ceb0ff3726edbef52832e5aa81da7418a1c251b7","tid":341971,"uid":16147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:32:12.000Z","msg":"做it 仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da89f4d489cea63fd75e857688ca18f2